data RawLogEntry timestamp attrib paragraph

A representation of entries in a raw-log file. We will make it more generic than needed so that we can reuse it later.

type UTCTimeStamp1970 = (Int, Integer)

Representation of UTC timestamp as two integer (o,t) where o is the location offset in minutes, and t is time in terms of elapses millisecond after midnight of 1st jan 1970.
